<h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold my-8">Why contribute?</h2>
<div class="grid grid-4 mb-4">
  <div class="card">
    <h3>Build Skills</h3>
    <p>Working on real-world projects exposes you to new technologies and best practices.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="card">
    <h3>Build Portfolio</h3>
    <p>Your contributions get recorded on GitHub, providing tangible proof of your skills.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="card">
    <h3>Build Network</h3>
    <p>Interacting with the community offers immense learning opportunities and widens your professional network.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="card">
    <h3>Build Community</h3>
    <p>By contributing, you help grow the local tech scene and create a richer environment for everyone involved.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold my-8">How to contribute?</h2>
<div class="grid grid-4 mb-4">
  <div class="card">
    <h3>Join the Conversation</h3>
    <p>Join us <a href="https://slack.devict.org" class="link-blue">in Slack</a> and jump into the conversation! Share what you're working on, ask questions, and help others.</p>
    <a href="https://slack.devict.org/" class="btn">Join Slack</a>
  </div>
  <div class="card">
    <h3>Contribute to a Project</h3>
    <p>Browse our <a href="https://github.com/devict" class="link-blue">GitHub organization</a> to find projects you can contribute to. Plenty of ways to help with or without coding.</p>
    <a href="https://github.com/devict" class="btn">Get Coding</a>
  </div>
  <div class="card">
    <h3>Give a Talk or Workshop</h3>
    <p>Share your knowledge and experience in a lightning talk or more comprehensive sessions.</p>
    <a href="mailto:seth@devict.org" class="btn">Reach Out</a>
  </div>
  <div class="card">
    <h3>Support Financially</h3>
    <p>Donations help us keep the lights on and fund community events. Every bit counts!</p>
    <a href="/support/" class="btn">Donate</a>
  </div>
</div>

